title: Kendall Jenner, Ciara, Demi Moore and More Stun at 'Harper's Bazaar' Event Honoring Fashionable Women
text: Kendall Jenner, Ciara, Demi Moore and More Stun at 'Harper's Bazaar' Event Honoring Fashionable Women by Desiree Murphy 12:40   Photo: Getty Images Slay, all day! A slew of stylish stars attended Harper's Bazaar 's 150 Most Fashionable Women event at the Sunset Tower Hotel in West Hollywood, California, on Friday, stepping out in fierce ensembles. Kendall Jenner wore a black-and-nude sheer La Perla gown, styling the sexy frock with strappy black heels and a silver choker. Photo: Getty Images Ciara, who is pregnant with husband Russell Wilson's first child and her second, put her baby bump on full display, rocking a gorgeous off-the-shoulder black velvet gown by Rhea Costa. The singer looked simply stunning, opting for sheer straight hair and a bronzed glow. Photo: Getty Images Fifth Harmony's Lauren Jauregui also donned a velvet number, pairing her beautiful burgundy Jocelyn dress with a sparkly choker and Jimmy Choo heels. Photo: Getty Images But who says you need to wear a dress to impress? Chanel Iman proved pants can be just as chic when paired with strappy stilettos and dainty jewelry. Photo: Getty Images Meanwhile, Julianne Hough put her own glam take on the trendy jumpsuit, sporting a silver-and-black Zuhair Murad one-piece embellished with sparkles. She highlighted her petite waist with a chunky metallic belt, completing the look with black Giuseppe Zanotti heels and an Edie Parker clutch. Photo: Getty Images And it was a family affair for Demi Moore, who stepped out with her youngest daughters, Tallulah and Scout. Photo: Getty Images Gorgeous!
